 agement\, and teaching  </li><li>Help faculty connect community-engaged t
 eaching to professional development and research  </li></ul><p>  The conf
 erence is seeking proposals for presentations\, roundtables\, and academi
 c posters from faculty\, community partners\, students\, and staff.<br />
