SUMMARY:Preview Screening of "Creating Resolve"
DESCRIPTION:This film explores the transformative power of creative resol
 ve in global health. From the frontlines of Rwanda's HIV fight to the his
 toric eradication of smallpox\, we go behind the scenes with the activist
 s and experts who refused to accept the status quo. It's more than a hist
 ory of medicine\; it's a blueprint for a future where health is a right\,
  not a privilege\, and international solidarity is our strongest vaccine.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  This film explores the transformative p
 ower of creative resolve in global health. From the frontlines of Rwanda'
 s HIV fight to the historic eradication of smallpox\, we go behind the sc
 enes with the activists and experts who refused to accept the status quo.
  It's more than a history of medicine\; it's a blueprint for a future whe
 re health is a right\, not a privilege\, and international solidarity is 
 our strongest vaccine.</p>
