 e: June 19</p><p><strong>Steps to Register:</strong></p><ol><li>Decide wh
 ether you want to enroll for credit (B504) or non-credit  </li><li><stron
 g>For Credit:</strong> Complete the pre-registration form\; once permissi
 on received\, register through standard IU course registration system  </
 li><li><strong>Non-Credit:</strong> [TBD]  </li></ol><p><strong>Questions
 ?</strong> Contact: Dr Elisheva Cohen\, <a href="mailto:ellcohen@iu.edu">
 ellcohen@iu.edu</a></p><h2>  Who Should Apply?</h2><p>  This program is i
 deal for Hamilton Lugar School undergraduates who are:</p><ul><li>Conside
 ring law school or legal careers  </li><li>Interested in policy\, interna
 tional relations\, or governance  </li><li>Seeking to build research and 
