SUMMARY:Hamilton Lugar School Commencement Recognition Ceremony
DESCRIPTION:Commencement: Hamilton Lugar School of Global and Internation
 al Studies: Indiana University Bloomington (https://hls.indiana.edu/comme
 ncement/index.html)Important: Two steps are required to attend:Complete t
 he Hamilton Lugar registration form (https://iu.co1.qualtrics.com/jfe/for
 m/SV_8jiK9aYN5m1707c).  Reserve your ticket through the Musical Arts Cent
 er ticketing page (https://hls.indiana.edu/commencement/am.ticketmaster.c
 om/iumac/buy/HLS2026).  In order to participate in commencement both step
 s must be completed by Friday\, April 24. Even if you do not have guests 
 attending commencement\, you still must register for one ticket through s
 tep #2.  Please note that the Musical Arts Center emails about ticketing 
 will come from "IU Opera and Ballet Theater".
