SUMMARY:Call Out Meeting: Short Term Study Abroad (Spring/Summer) 2027
DESCRIPTION:Come learn about HLS's short-term study abroad programs:Bruss
 els: European Union in Action (spring semester on campus + 10 days abroad
 )  Costa Rica: Global Perspectives on Central America (2 weeks in summer)
   Jordan: Introduction to Refugee Studies (8 week class on campus + 10 da
 ys abroad)  Uzbekistan: Central Asia in Soviet Times (spring semester on 
 campus + 10 days abroad)    For more information about our programs abroa
 d and to apply\, click here.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Come learn about HLS's short-term study
  abroad programs:</p><ul><li>Brussels: European Union in Action (spring s
 emester on campus + 10 days abroad)  </li><li>Costa Rica: Global Perspect
 ives on Central America (2 weeks in summer)  </li><li>Jordan: Introductio
 n to Refugee Studies (8 week class on campus + 10 days abroad)  </li><li>
 Uzbekistan: Central Asia in Soviet Times (spring semester on campus + 10 
 days abroad)  </li></ul><p>  For more information about our programs abro
 ad and to apply\, click here.</p>
